{"tid":509910,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"天降帳篷突襲傷腰 張振朗憂性能力　蔡思貝陪操","createTime":"2017-12-25T23:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T07:52:59.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e94a88233c97ccc8462e941f53e537cfa43c1117","tid":509910,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T23:51:28.000Z","msg":"天降帳篷突襲傷腰<br />\n張振朗憂性能力　<br />\n<br />\n蔡思貝陪張振朗於前晚平安夜飛來橫禍，被一個未有綁緊的帳篷整傷入院，昨日凌晨時分，他在面書上留言報平安，並上載坐救護車的照片，以及兩張相分別是兩個插在花槽邊反轉的帳篷，以及有三個男人拉着險跌落碼頭的帳篷，他留言：「一個不平安的平安夜，何解三個帳篷會在天台飛落街？為何沒有人把帳篷綁好？如果打中一個小朋友，他一定會冇命。」<br />\n<br />\n撐枴杖出活動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前晚已出院回家休息的張振朗，昨日和蔡思貝出席上水活動時，要撐着爬山枴杖行路，他說：「唔好彩整傷咗，𠵱家彎唔到腰，但慶幸就係冇傷到個樣，如果唔係都要退休。」<br />\n<br />\n活動後張振朗受訪說：「同謝東閔、另一個朋友去食嘢，去到一個地方，朋友大叫『小心呀，走呀！』，我未會意到係乜事，喺天台就有三個帳篷跌落嚟，撞到我條腰同膝頭哥，我瞓咗喺地下十幾分鐘都郁唔到，好唔開心。」會否追究責任？他說：「稍後研究，𠵱家睇番健康先，今晚都要開廠，但因為我彎唔到腰，所以打唔到，今日出活動我都要戴腰封，好似四哥，噚晚隻左腳郁唔到，今日郁到，但要戴護膝。」張振朗更謂擔心劇集《包青天再起風雲》被易角。<br />\n<br />\n女友不在現場<br />\n<br />\n至於女友陳芷尤有否關心他？張振朗說：「有，但佢當時唔在場。」問會否怕腰傷變成舊患？他說：「好驚會影響生育能力，我唔想。」身旁的蔡思貝表示可為他做替身，可以不眠不休狂操，張振朗即取笑是「女版成龍」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20171226/20255265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F20255265&d=uBAeJpYWmU%2Bax4UVActdkBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c7d79de1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F20255265&h=c7a31a29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20171226/20255265</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/075042_a271c6e7ff424254698204f499871260.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F075042_a271c6e7ff424254698204f499871260.jpeg&h=ab988c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n能成為密友大概都帶著愛"},{"pid":"8665348a306f36450176d7ff7d3015cb42ab0f9a","tid":509910,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:06:46.000Z","msg":"乜都關蔡思貝事<br />\n佢係咪覺得撬走靚女條仔有勝利感？<br />\nyoyo 大波尤"},{"pid":"4f56de5d16cec9a1151ff4ac71f63b689d61640f","tid":509910,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a510281a37f4b9f187bf748a96c2dec6017a90a","tid":509910,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:12:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾關我撚事？"},{"pid":"05245cd59eb0fda5a1da46216748b63e78501568","tid":509910,"uid":158977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:13:19.000Z","msg":"達哥真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢做朋友冇得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35826514c30dead790ee897883f2199b7565057","tid":509910,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f56de5d16cec9a1151ff4ac71f63b689d61640f","tid":509910,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"呢張唔似達哥喎"},{"pid":"1e0b04dfe451e5ed9a392e457f59954ecc725318","tid":509910,"uid":24696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:53:37.000Z","msg":"蔡思達<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d5ece46e1f3f1020318827b1c0bd902754ccb6","tid":509910,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd2400197e1b8e5a284494c8d1961446f780a9ae","tid":509910,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a510281a37f4b9f187bf748a96c2dec6017a90a","tid":509910,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:12:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾關我撚事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"香港地係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h